::DarkMouse::

"YES Megatron.  I shall remain here and hold down the base."

She didn't like the whole idea of being in charge, but it's not like she had 
a choice in the matter.

She went to the console and armed the auto-systems for anything that wasn't 
in the computer's signature system.

She watched on the screen and hoped the Scorponok would be careful.
"OH, be careful."

She just waited at  her post.
